                                INTRODUCTION

    The Vidi-AMIGA ia a complete colour video digitiser in one unit for use
with the following AMIGA computers:

    A500(+), A600, A1200, A1500, A2000, A3000, A4000.

    It can be used to produce images in various combinations of screen modes 
and resolutions.
 
                              PACKAGE CONTAINS

    You should find:
   
    Vidi-AMIGA 12 digitiser unit,
    Software disk,
    Manual,
    Phono - Phono vide cable,
    Registration card.

    If any of the aboce itms are missing please contact your dealer.

