    If after these tests the Vidi-AMIGA unit still appears to be
malfunctioning the if possible try the Vidi-AMIGA on another machine, just
to confirm that there is not a fault on your computer.
    Lastly phone or write to the ROMBO technical supportline.

    Note: It is perfectly possible for an Amiga to have a faulty parallel
